same result as SGD, but the SGLD optimizer behaves a little wried, at first the validation-accuracy raises to nearly 50% then it will decrease, and finally get to nearly 10%. I have followed the python
implemetation and could not figure out where is the problem.

Hi @Ldpe2G I trained the model in Python and now is going to deploy it in Java environment, but encountered some difficulties, could you give me a hint?

The model file is said to be language agnostic, so I write a predict function in Java as below:

``` Java
public void predict(NDArrayIter dataiter, int batchSize) {

    SGD opt = new SGD(0.0001f, 0.9f, 0.000f, 0.0f, null);
